snippet.title: Alnico Smithery Teaser
snippet.description:
Coming to Early Access October 25th!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2381060/Alnico_Smithery/

Alnico Smithery is a hand-drawn, physics-based forging simulator. Mine for ore, smelt ingots, discover alloys, forge tools, and rebuild the smithery your grandfather left behind.

Follow the development of the game in the official Discord server! https://discord.gg/GtkDQjChze
